# d3-core conventions

- Treat `src/d3-core/` as the **rendering engine**: keep it deterministic and fast.
- Avoid per-frame allocations in hot paths (scales, axes generation, series transforms).
- Prefer precomputing derived series data outside React render and passing in minimal inputs.
- Keep chart primitives composable; avoid coupling to container/layout state.
- When adding chart types, follow the existing `src/d3-core/charts/*` structure and reuse shared utilities.

